response.overview: A detective discovers that a treacherous bear has murdered her husband. She is apprehended, taken to court, and sentenced to life in prison. Though she escapes and is on the run, her location is discovered by Great Chief Chubb, chief of the Downtown Zacklyn Police Force. Only through a fierce battle will there be Justice...
response.tagline: In a World of Crime, there is always Criminals...
response.title: Cliché Cop Movie 1
